<h3><span id="clothing">Clothing</span>
</h3>
<h4><span id="jacket-and-pants">Jacket and pants</span>
</h4>
<p>Jacket and pants as top layers protect you from the elements, so focus on solid waterproofing. For the resort riding you should be generally ok with <b>10k waterproofing and breathability</b> unless you live in a very wet climate. For freeriding you might want to go to 20k and up (GORE-TEX&reg;, eVent&trade; and other materials) if your budget allows it</p>
<p>When it comes to insulation, a good compromise for resort riding is a light insulation in the jacket. For freeriding technical, non-insulated jackets are a better choice.</p>
<div id="attachment_4901" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
<a href="https://us.oneill.com/products/9p0004-7970-textured-jacket"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-4901" class="size-full wp-image-4901 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="O'Neill Textured Jacket" width="780" height="760" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== 1w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-src="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020.jpg 780w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020-765x745.jpg 765w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020-610x594.jpg 610w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020-460x448.jpg 460w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020-348x339.jpg 348w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/oneill-textured-2020-260x253.jpg 260w"></a><p id="caption-attachment-4901" class="wp-caption-text"><a href="https://us.oneill.com/products/9p0004-7970-textured-jacket">O&rsquo;Neill Textured Jacket</a></p>
</div>
<p>Especially as a beginner you may sit on ground more often so pay attention to choosing quality pants.</p>
<p>Snowboarding jackets should have a powder skirt inside, which prevents snow from getting to your waist and can be attached to your pants. Volcom offers a patented <a href="https://www.volcom.com/blogs/truetothis/zip-tech-outerwear-technology">jacket-to-pant zip feature</a>.</p>
<p>A good alternative are bib pants because they provide a good protection against snow and also allow the free movement of the waist.</p>
<div id="attachment_4903" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
<a href="https://www.dcshoes.com/revival-snow-bib-pants-191282539699.html"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-4903" class="size-full wp-image-4903 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="DC Revival Snow Bib Pants" width="780" height="819" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== 1w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-src="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020.jpg 780w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020-765x803.jpg 765w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020-610x641.jpg 610w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020-460x483.jpg 460w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020-348x365.jpg 348w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dc-revival-2020-260x273.jpg 260w"></a><p id="caption-attachment-4903" class="wp-caption-text"><a href="https://www.dcshoes.com/revival-snow-bib-pants-191282539699.html">Revival Snow Bib Pants</a> from DC</p>
</div>
<p>When it comes to style, jacket and pants usually come in three styles:</p>
<ul>
<li>loose fit</li>
<li>standard fit</li>
<li>slim fit</li>
</ul>
<p>Choose the fit you like but ensure that any protective gear you use fits under it. As a beginner you might want to pick standard to loose fit for freedom of movement. What can feel a bit baggy and oversized doesn&rsquo;t feel like that much when riding. This is especially true for the pants which need relatively big leg openings to fit over the boots. Also make sure that your pants are long enough even when you squat.</p>
<p>Check out <a href="https://www.evo.com/guides/outerwear-fit-jacket-length-guide">Evo&rsquo;s guide on outerwear fit</a>.</p>
<h4><span id="gloves">Gloves</span>
</h4>
<p>For gloves you have two options &ndash; <b>mitts </b>and <b>gloves</b>. Mitts are more popular among snowboarders as they will keep your hands warmer. They may make it a bit harder to operate things like your zips or bindings buckles, though.</p>
<div id="attachment_4905" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
<a href="https://crabgrab.com/collections/mittens/products/copy-of-snuggler-mitt?variant=19447703863382"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-4905" class="size-full wp-image-4905 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Snuggler Mitt by Crab Grab" width="780" height="948" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== 1w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-src="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020.jpg 780w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020-765x930.jpg 765w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020-610x741.jpg 610w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020-460x559.jpg 460w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020-348x423.jpg 348w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/crab-grab-mitts-2020-260x316.jpg 260w"></a><p id="caption-attachment-4905" class="wp-caption-text"><a href="https://crabgrab.com/collections/mittens/products/copy-of-snuggler-mitt?variant=19447703863382">Snuggler Mitt</a> by Crab Grab</p>
</div>
<p>Ensure that your gloves are easy to take off and put on, especially if you plan to use wrist protection. If they go under your jacket sleeve check out that your sleeve has enough room to fit them under.</p>
<h4><span id="base-and-mid-layers">Base and mid layers</span>
</h4>
<p>The base layer should be from functional material to keep you warm and dry. You can try a one-piece bottom layer for extra warmth.</p>
<div id="attachment_4907" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
<a href="https://myairblaster.com/products/womens-merino-ninja-suit?variant=29645880492120"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-4907" class="size-full wp-image-4907 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Airblaster Women&rsquo;s Merino Ninja Suit" width="780" height="917" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== 1w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-src="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020.jpg 780w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020-765x899.jpg 765w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020-610x717.jpg 610w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020-460x541.jpg 460w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020-348x409.jpg 348w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-suit-2020-260x306.jpg 260w"></a><p id="caption-attachment-4907" class="wp-caption-text">One-piece base layers are becoming more and more popular. <a href="https://myairblaster.com/products/womens-merino-ninja-suit?variant=29645880492120">Women&rsquo;s Merino Ninja Suit</a> by Airblaster</p>
</div>
<p>Depending on whether your jacket is insulated or not, you can pick up a hoodie or inner layer jacket.</p>
<div id="attachment_4909" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
<a href="https://www.burton.com/us/en/p/womens-oak-full-zip-hoodie/W19-164421.html"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-4909" class="size-full wp-image-4909 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Burton Oak Full-Zip Hoodie" width="780" height="730" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== 1w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-src="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020.jpg 780w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020-765x716.jpg 765w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020-610x571.jpg 610w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020-460x431.jpg 460w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020-348x326.jpg 348w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/burton-hoodie-2020-260x243.jpg 260w"></a><p id="caption-attachment-4909" class="wp-caption-text">Women&rsquo;s <a href="https://www.burton.com/us/en/p/womens-oak-full-zip-hoodie/W19-164421.html">Oak Full-Zip Hoodie</a> by Burton</p>
</div>
<h4><span id="facemask">Facemask</span>
</h4>
<p>A facemask, balaclava, or neck warmer is a must on the snowboard. It will keep snow and wind out of your face and neck.</p>
<div id="attachment_4911" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
<a href="https://myairblaster.com/products/merino-ninja-face?variant=29915378876504"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-4911" class="size-full wp-image-4911 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="Airblaster Merino Ninja Face" width="780" height="600" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw== 1w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-src="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020.jpg" data-srcset="https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020.jpg 780w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020-765x588.jpg 765w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020-610x469.jpg 610w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020-460x354.jpg 460w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020-348x268.jpg 348w, https://www.xfive.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/airblaster-ninja-face-2020-260x200.jpg 260w"></a><p id="caption-attachment-4911" class="wp-caption-text"><a href="https://myairblaster.com/products/merino-ninja-face?variant=29915378876504">Merino Ninja Face</a> by Airblaster</p>
</div>
<h4><span id="socks">Socks</span>
</h4>
<p>Thinner socks can keep your feet warmer than thick socks, which tend to pack up in the boots and reduce blood circulation. Choose socks from synthetic materials or wool (for example Merino Wool) which keeps warm even when wet.</p>
<div id="attachment_4913" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
