<h3><span id="protection">Protection</span>
</h3>
<h4><span id="goggles">Goggles</span>
</h4>
<p>Goggles should offer a good peripheral vision and fit your face without any discomfort. They are often sold with two pairs of glasses &ndash; one for low light condition and another one for sunny days.</p>
<div id="attachment_4919" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
