</h4>
<p>A helmet is <i>a must for a beginner</i> on a snowboard. Catching the edge is one of the most common reasons of fall &ndash; slamming your head against the snow is not fun.</p>
<p>If you don&rsquo;t like the look of a helmet consider wearing your goggles under the helmet for a more stylish look. In any case avoid a gap between the goggles and helmet.</p>
