<h4><span id="wrist-guards">Wrist guards</span>
</h4>
<p>Wrist injuries are quite common among snowboarders. When you fall down you instinctively try to reduce impact by using your hands &ndash; instead, try spread out impact by using your forearms (see Common mistakes in the next section for more details).</p>
