</div>
<h3><span id="how-to-improve-your-riding">How to improve your riding</span>
</h3>
<p>Snowboard Addiction has another nice video summarizing all common mistakes and tips on how to improve your riding</p>
<div>
<div class="c-embed c-embed--video"><iframe title="How To Improve Your Riding On A Snowboard" width="500" height="281" src="about:blank" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen class=" lazyload" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qsd8uaex-Is?feature=oembed"></iframe></div>
