</div>
<p>Check out Snowboard Addiction&rsquo;s <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TPvkUAVIOIA&amp;list=PLBMGwWHdh0Eb9WSYaKUlgx0WZzZtm51nh">buttering trick playlist</a> for many variations of butter tricks.</p>
<p>It&rsquo;s easier to butter on softer snowboards, just in case you wonder why you may have trouble doing butters on a stiff, freeride board.</p>
