<h4><span id="jibbing">Jibbing</span>
</h4>
<p>Jibbing is the most technical form of freestyle snowboarding. It means sliding with your snowboard on boxes or handrails. You can slide on these features with snowboard parallel to them (50-50) or perpendicular (boardslides) or combine them in various ways. You can jump into and out of the features using rotation and counter rotation and use presses. This creates endless combinations.</p>
