<h2><span id="conclusion">Conclusion</span>
</h2>
<p>Snowboarding is for everyone and it&rsquo;s never too late to start with it &ndash; maybe you will find a new passion in your life.</p>
<p>Snowboarding is also yours. It means that it&rsquo;s only up to you what form and shape you give to your riding. Take others as inspiration but find your unique way &ndash; there is always space for progress, no matter what your current level is.</p>
